SecuredMe License Family

This repository defines two custom educational license texts:

- Secured Educational License 2.0: SEL-2.0
- Secured Educational Cybersecurity License 2.0: SECL-2.0

See:

- `LICENSE-SEL-2.0`
- `LICENSE-SECL-2.0`

Both licenses are custom SecuredMe licenses. They are not currently
OSI-approved licenses and are not currently listed in the SPDX License List.
LicenseRef-SEL-2.0 and LicenseRef-SECL-2.0 may be used only as local metadata
references when the full selected license text is included in the target
repository.

